Tapas, a Spanish tradition of small plates, has become a popular way to enjoy food with friends and family around the world. A Tapas Board is a perfect way to serve these small plates and create a feast for the senses. Whether you’re hosting a casual gathering or a fancy dinner party, a Tapas Board offers a wide variety of flavours, textures, and colours that everyone can enjoy. Make your own Summer Pesto Sharing Tapas Board with this recipe compliments of McCain. Prep Time: 10 minutes | Total Time: 35 minutes | Servings: 4 – 6 Sides: